                <h1>Explore the Rich History of Portland, Oregon</h1>
                <p>Portland, Oregon, was founded in 1845 by settlers who arrived via the Oregon Trail. Originally a trading hub due to its strategic location along the Willamette River, it flourished during the Gold Rush. Over the years, Portland grew into a vibrant city known for its culture, sustainability efforts, and thriving arts scene.</p>
